{"tid":695842,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)美國眾神","createTime":"2018-06-09T14:13:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T20:06:28.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a3e1929e8eecf9209c7dba2f2a33553338b05384","tid":695842,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T14:13:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">播唔完下次播返</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=TM1NSpFlEb2zKV9rxSrzWo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=1dafa8d3\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=TM1NSpFlEb2zKV9rxSrzWo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=8b90e54a\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=TM1NSpFlEb2zKV9rxSrzWo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=e6abfed7\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://lekturaobowiazkowa.pl/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/American_Gods_CharacterArt_MrWednesday_Amazon.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flekturaobowiazkowa.pl%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2FAmerican_Gods_CharacterArt_MrWednesday_Amazon.jpg&h=b518c5c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dramaqueen.com.tw/features/20170509/001.html \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dramaqueen.com.tw%2Ffeatures%2F20170509%2F001.html%20&d=TM1NSpFlEb2zKV9rxSrzWo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=c55edc86\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dramaqueen.com.tw/features/20170509/001.html </a> &lt;角色介紹<br />\n原著小說於2001年出版，先後被翻譯成30多種語言，在全球廣為流傳。故事描述一場即將到來的戰爭，對立的雙方是聖經故事和神話傳說中的「古代眾神」和代表新世界的「美國眾神」。<br />\n該劇描述在監牢中的男主角─影，等待著有天可以出獄，望向藍天，重回妻子、好友的懷抱。某天，一條消息到來，他可以提前兩天出獄，但卻是因為他的愛妻和好友同時車禍身亡，出獄後的他失去了一切，除了自由。從監獄釋放後，穿越美國大陸的旅行過程中的一系列奇遇。講述了他與生活在美國土地上的各種神祇相遇，由此引發了出許多精彩動人、奇詭絢麗的故事<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=TM1NSpFlEb2zKV9rxSrzWo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=f87ee5df\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=TM1NSpFlEb2zKV9rxSrzWo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=4e479f62\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"585c17f677570c6aa88251b98ff51cd132f95cb8","tid":695842,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T16:23:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"807396ba14f67cb6c4b849aebb7bcb85daf95798","tid":695842,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T17:03:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" c